  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*:  carer in field \"Type a mesage\" moves to several chars inside of text when you are typing fast.\r\nSame as https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/5670 but in another field.\r\nDidn't notice the same behavior on other fields.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ncaret is always in the end of the phrase\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\ncaret is moved in the middle of the text\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open 1-1 chat\r\n- Type message (fast)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: status nightly 27/09/18\r\n* Operating System: Mac OSx\r\n* Video: http://take.ms/pDHBk\r\n\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://api.monosnap.com/rpc/file/download?id=IGmMJt0lEfhFnoknzbV5ksjcssXprx&type=preview\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div>Monosnap screenshot tool</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://monosnap.com/file/IGmMJt0lEfhFnoknzbV5ksjcssXprx\">File \"screencast 2018-09-27 18-15-31.mp4\"</a></strong></div><div>Monosnap â€” the best tool to take & share your screenshots.</div></blockquote>",
